metadata.description: Frat Bears Fratstars are the pioneers of the fratbears ecosystem. A Frat Bear NFT provides you not only an awesome PFP, but also a membership to our Chapter , which gives you access to IRL events like Frat parties, Mastermind Events, Exclusive Merch, and did we mention Frat Parties ??? Cuz who would want to join a fraternity without the parties (TBA) . all of this is only for Version 1.0 of our roadmap. Ready to be Initiated?
